          "children": [
            {
              "marks": [],
              "_key": "080f081d4f7f",
              "text": "Click on the plus sign as you would to add any other step and select ",
              "_type": "span"
            },
            {
              "_key": "f68cdd43cd50",
              "text": "Checkpoint",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [ "code" ]
            },
            {
              "_key": "4ab04dc6f8bc",
              "text": ". Choose between waiting for an ",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": []
            },
            {
              "_key": "9e9df5bcf56d",
              "text": "Event",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [ "code" ]
            },
            {
              "_key": "3076a6e7bfdb",
              "text": " in an app to happen or a specific amount of time (",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": []
            },
            {
              "_key": "6eea23100deb",
              "text": "Delay",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [ "code" ]
            },
            {
              "marks": [],
              "_key": "5600c48535e2",
              "text": ").",
              "_type": "span"
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": []
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "marks": [],
              "_key": "910158203fbb",
              "text": "If you’ve chosen to wait for an event, you need to click continue or go to the ",
              "_type": "span"
            },
            {
              "_key": "d34020ba61de",
              "text": "Connection",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [ "code" ]
            },
            {
              "_key": "fe05b77c6320",
              "text": " tab, then select the app, the type of event, your connection and the ID for the exact object to monitor — if you are awaiting a project to be completed, you can specify the project ID so your Flight only continues once this specific project is completed.",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": []
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": [],
          "_key": "b9dd37a31c6a",
          "_type": "block",
          "style": "normal"
        },
        {
          "_key": "bda8ac4d4827",
          "_type": "block",
          "style": "normal",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "If the Delay option was selected instead, you need to specify the amount of time to wait in the ",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "_key": "ee8e7d0075e7"
            },
            {
              "_key": "b57e11bec50b",
              "text": "Duration",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [ "code" ]
            },
            {
              "_key": "c5783820ec7d",
              "text": " tab.",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": []
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
